          "rationale": "This book follows the events leading up to, during, and after the Civil War through the life of Abraham Lincoln.  As students read about Lincoln’s personal and public struggles, students will learn about the character and leadership of this man during one of the most tumultuous times of our nation’s history. This is the first war during which photography was used to show the people back home what war was really like, so the images capture not only the events, but also the new technology of the age.",
